Package: easypar
Type: Package
Title: Easy parallaleization of R functions
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Giulio Caravagna
Maintainer: Giulio Caravagna <gcaravagn@gmail.com>
Authors@R: person("Giulio", "Caravagna", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "gcaravagn@gmail.com")
Description: This package allows to run R functions in a parallel way in a easy fashion, masking
  all the subtle aspects of writing parallel code, and allowing to switch at runtime from parallel
  to sequential runs of a piece of code without effort.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
  doParallel,
  parallel,
  foreach
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/caravagn/easypar
BugReports: https://github.com/caravagn/easypar/issues
